attributes.PROJECT_FULL_TITLE: Interconnection between Gatica (ES) and Cubnezais (FR) [currently known as "Biscay Gulf"]
attributes.TECHNICAL_DESCR: A new 400 kV HVDC subsea cable interconnection of approximately 394 km with a capacity of 2x1000 MW between Nouvelle Aquitaine and the Basque country, via the Biscay Gulf (offshore), with VCS converters at the end.
attributes.PROMOTERS: RTE - Réseau de Transport d'Electricité (FR) ; REE - Red Eléctrica de España S.A.U. (ES)
